name: 'Inspiration Dawning 2', 2021
description: 'Inspiration Dawning 2' is my second-ever NFT. I feel so fortunate when my muse comes around. This piece is a part of my digital abstract series. Like all of them, my digital abstracts begin life as photographs and I go from there, and I believe these digital abstracts to be photographs. File: 11.9MB PNG, 3675 × 2453.
